{"tid":2258324,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"肥亨 中大 劉正 咩學歷？","createTime":"2020-10-26T03:07:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T05:28:07.000Z","uid":338262,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"5657a2a23fbdd188409e25f254dea393b612d635","tid":2258324,"uid":338262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T03:07:58.000Z","msg":"有冇詳細資料？"},{"pid":"7ecc105ea8568cb7f1b6cc5b60c065ab7d00e56d","tid":2258324,"uid":55458,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T03:10:43.000Z","msg":"黃洋達1979年出生於香港，祖籍廣東海豐縣公平鎮，有柬埔寨血統，是鶴佬人。父輩一代來港，後來由新界搬到九龍彩虹邨長大。中學就讀可立中學，中四時父親去世，之後於姑母家中長大。黃父曾在中國大陸因文革坐牢10年，讓黃洋達印象深刻[3]。其後考入香港浸會大學傳理學院電視電影專業（現稱「電影學院」），曾為浸大辯論隊成員。"},{"pid":"7ca89d6b55ff80383564727ecd42b50673d7259d","tid":2258324,"uid":366245,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T03:11:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e9564a99599f7d94255b0574f4761d9c20229245","tid":2258324,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T03:12:27.000Z","msg":"中大碩士囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fcb9c888925474301af6cc8460baeed81d85820","tid":2258324,"uid":313426,"like":14,"dislike":4,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"5657a2a23fbdd188409e25f254dea393b612d635","tid":2258324,"uid":338262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T03:07:58.000Z","msg":"有冇詳細資料？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T17:57:34.000Z","msg":"劉正 (= 無神論者的巴別塔，高級狗夫）大學讀歷史系，而家教日研。<br />\n<br />\n唔好話無 Phd 啦，MPhil都畢唔到業，搞到要送個MA 俾佢。taught master，周街都係啦。<br />\n教日本研究，但啲人話佢唔識日文，唔知點樣教日研。<br />\n可能以為睇AV 打下飛機 嗚啊嗚啊嗚啊嗚啊嗚啊就係識日本文化。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J86orTy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ86orTy.jpg&h=cd6f998e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中大劉正呢啲呃教席誤人子弟嘅垃圾，收皮啦。<br />\n<br />\n附中大學棍劉正撚樣圖一張"},{"pid":"ea5cff841d57adea3879a39fdcdb23432959cbda","tid":2258324,"uid":338262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fcb9